{"tid":1303964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開卷有益]警察通例你要識！","createTime":"2019-07-10T13:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T15:34:48.000Z","uid":108757,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"256c9544cf0c5d240ff493bf5ecd5536e47cb48f","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"近日，香港警察於大型示威遊行期間，出現大量違規情況。一般小市民無法得知警隊內部有何指引，而警隊網頁只得<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小量</span></span>有關警方權力規範的資料。縱使資料有限，但警方於一個月內已違反數十條《警察通例》中的規例，市民有責任作出監督及投訴。<br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》第1章第2條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fzjw36a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzjw36a.jpg&h=bbbcf162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《警察通例》根據香港法例第232章第46條制定，條例規定所有警務人員必須遵守《警察通例》。<br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》 第6章第1條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQJ58za.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQJ58za.jpg&h=dfea496a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於示威期間，多名警員不合理使用武力， 明顯<span style=\"color: red;\">失去自我節制能力</span>，亦公然違反此條例。<br />\n於7月7日九意區遊行期間，警員進入地盤搬運鐵枝及磚塊，企圖與<span style=\"color: red;\">不良分子作出可疑行為</span>，公然違反此條例。<br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》 第6章第1(34)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAhR4aq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAhR4aq.jpg&h=b4c93dd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SF2VMoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSF2VMoL.jpg&h=ed09bed3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n於7月5日，警察評議會職方協會去信英國工黨議員古德曼，要求古德曼向該警司及警隊道歉。及於7月8日，警察員佐級協會發聲明，向立法會主席梁君彥投訴泛民立法會議員。顯然地，該兩個協會<span style=\"color: red;\">非因執行職務參與政治活動</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">違反政治中立</span>，亦公然違反此條例。<br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》 第6章第1(31)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08aAkW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08aAkW.jpg&h=35470c66&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n於6月12日金鐘集會期間，警員多次對市民作出恐嚇及威脅性言辭，包括向記者高叫「記你老母」，對在場宗教人士高呼「叫你耶穌落嚟見我」，及對示威人士呼喊「自由閪」，以上種種乃<span style=\"color: red;\">不當的行為舉止</span>，嚴重損害警隊聲譽。<br />\n於7月7日旺角清場行動時，多名警員穿著T-Shirt及短褲執行職務，其<span style=\"color: red;\">衣著及儀表明顯不恰當</span>，公然違反此條例。<br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》 第6章第1(44)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzfPQXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzfPQXK.jpg&h=96422912&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n於7月7日旺角清場行動時，有市民遭警員無理阻截，並在<span style=\"color: red;\">不合理情況下</span>要求市民解鎖手機，在<span style=\"color: red;\">市民多次拒絕</span>下，警員仍<span style=\"color: red;\">強行逼使市民解鎖</span>。警員更威脅市民不要向外透露其無理搜查，<span style=\"color: red;\">否則警員有權公開市民的住址</span>。以上行為明顯在得不到市民的同意下作出<span style=\"color: red;\">強行搜查</span>，其後更<span style=\"color: red;\">企圖對市民的個人資料作非法用途</span>，公然違反此條例。<br />\n<br />\n寫住咁多先。目前，各位如要投訴，在沒有獨立調查委員會下，暫時只能向監警會投訴。雖然監警會能力受質疑，但市民仍要作出投訴。因為現時監警會收到的投訴個案只有數十個，政府便有理由推搪成立獨立調查委員會沒有必要，但若然投訴數字大幅上升，對成立委員會便有更大說服力。最低限度可以令監警會有關人士為處理投訴疲於奔命。但投訴人<span style=\"color: red;\">必須注意</span>，投訴前必須考慮自身安全，<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自身安全情況</span></span>下，向監警會作出投訴，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只提供有限度的個人資料</span></span>作聯絡用途。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自身安全情況</span></span>下，向監警會作出投訴，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只提供有限度的個人資料</span></span>作聯絡用途。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自身安全情況</span></span>下，向監警會作出投訴，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只提供有限度的個人資料</span></span>作聯絡用途。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎市民繼續研究《警察通例》。<br />\n<br />\n監警會聯絡方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/other/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fother%2Fcontact_us.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=fb665287\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/other/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5kDKmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5kDKmK.jpg&h=0cddb854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n供公眾查閱的警察通例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Fpgo.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=10a5d4ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html</a>"},{"pid":"032f8281c4e67dd35c184fca68d649d3acb72a2c","tid":1303964,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"香港人要背書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>NOW</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30</span></span><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=7b0d7f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=bb35c405\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<strong>7.12</strong> - <ins>光復港大 守衛我城</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=7e28ec57\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n<strong>7.13</strong> - <ins>光復上水</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=db685cd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32eEvRm</a><br />\n<strong>7.14</strong> - <ins>沙田區大遊行</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst7142019&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=897ab9a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/st7142019</a><br />\n<strong>7.27</strong> - <ins>紅磡土瓜灣大遊行</ins> - 待確認<br />\n<strong>7.28</strong> - <ins>將軍澳遊行</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=3aea2f02\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/tko728</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>抵制TVB</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=4dc49981\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>美國聯署 人權民主法案</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9bf3dc0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n</span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化</em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有信用評分之後 痴memo 遊行 上網講錯嘢 信錯教都可能扣你分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請不要再裝睡 行動吧香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得簽聯署呀!!!香港人權和民主法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=f4f2e649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n捐款支持「香港民意研究所」讓數據說實話，讓數據揭真相。： <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=1a590f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBAj6Qv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBAj6Qv.gif&h=8056e3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOJO3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOJO3Q.gif&h=92e11c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtUVJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtUVJR.gif&h=eaa393bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLA4yvw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLA4yvw.gif&h=3a86806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFOqhXb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFOqhXb.gif&h=b24b8c4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再提 捐款民調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc04041304bc4559b8a81731a2cd7aef4294ed3","tid":1303964,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"下次發夢我一定會印定哂D警察通例開大聲公讀出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82995a7bac15e57e8ded96623c0c41e2465fe8d","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第15章第1條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j92KEZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj92KEZF.jpg&h=f6defcfb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n於7月7日旺角清場行動中，有警員Wave sir (見圖示)穿著<span style=\"color: red;\">便服</span>及戴上頭盔執行職務，顯然在此條例中違反<span style=\"color: red;\">「不能夾雜制服和便服」</span>一條，其衣著及行為公然違反指引。<br />\n＿<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LwD2rEY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLwD2rEY.png&h=eb5b2594&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291e6a04581e1a2d66eb0996a1bee85516ec8219","tid":1303964,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3df31e967b4aff4959abb6bb601629da6c9c7ae5","tid":1303964,"uid":75664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"監警都係佢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f420b56a525bbcbef63ef477607cd2613181e0d8","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第15章第4條及第31條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3J2rGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3J2rGP.jpg&h=65ee82f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上述Wave sir 一事亦顯示該名警員同時違反第4條，<span style=\"color: red;\">軍裝警必須穿著制服當值</span>。<br />\n而當時在場之督導人員，任由警員公然違反守則，並沒有盡力確保其轄下人員的衣著及儀客符合要求，因此在場<span style=\"color: red;\">高級警員或指揮官</span>，亦同時違反第31條。"},{"pid":"7e4508352f97b42e04aa55daa5dad9d2a165e178","tid":1303964,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c4d0c1b6bb95351feb2e54df48083d18c48c326","tid":1303964,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:24:29.000Z","msg":"3.  《警察通例》對全體警務人員均適用，除非： <br />\n <br />\n  (a)  某條《警察通例》顯示相反目的；或 <br />\n <br />\n  (b)  《警察通例》內容抵觸了《基本法》、任何法律條例、規則、附例或<br />\n根據某條例制訂或頒布而警務人員須遵守的指令的條款；或 <br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>  (c)  某人員的僱用條件使他可免受《警察通例》的約束。 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大陸僱佣兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabc3b711c0a09a4a32007cf61c799add86c17cf","tid":1303964,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH!"},{"pid":"f164314341775bd2349f2aa6d858b799ac1a181a","tid":1303964,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"78dda844bc3ade2821e4813bd42ee9acf7bfe250","tid":1303964,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"算罷，假如一國一制之後，大陸一貫做法會將香港警察調去大陸西北或自動離職，取而代之係大陸公安同官員，到時香港全用大陸法律，因為大陸好驚地方人員造反。"},{"pid":"8d5fa6204c9cc1a699637694c418963f2930a88d","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第18章第3(3)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4QoVCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4QoVCM.jpg&h=810fcf93&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49nCfEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49nCfEk.jpg&h=2c9cd6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在7月7日九龍區遊行期間，有警員將警車駛入附近地盤，將大量鐵枝及磚塊搬上警車，行為可疑。第18章規定所有警車只可用作執行警隊職務，而<span style=\"color: red;\">警員不是地盤工人，搬運鐵枝及磚塊顯然不是警隊職務</span>。因此，該行動明顯違反此條例，屬<span style=\"color: red;\">濫用政府車輛</span>。"},{"pid":"f26f74c7e7633c812088b3db59e7070ecc452f7d","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"因為現時監警會收到的投訴個案<span style=\"color: red;\">只有數十個</span>，政府便<span style=\"color: red;\">有理由推搪成立獨立調查委員會沒有必要</span>，但若然投訴數字大幅上升，對成立委員會便有<span style=\"color: red;\">更大說服力</span>。"},{"pid":"595f0dcf2d28951c842e75e1a4df9aa39cf00e1e","tid":1303964,"uid":249526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4be9a7d847cf16177f310eba9d6ad8790e392fe6","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第20章第14條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Tz5pyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Tz5pyB.jpg&h=cfbce986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nF8580g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnF8580g.jpg&h=cbb32c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaXFXUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaXFXUj.jpg&h=73f746c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《警察通例》規定所有警務人員必須攜帶委任證，以證明其警員身份。<br />\n於6月12日金鐘集會期間，警方清場時派出速龍小隊驅散示威者，惟其服飾上<span style=\"color: red;\">欠缺警員編號</span>，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">未能提供委任證</span>，公然違反守則。<br />\n於6月21日警察總部外集會，期間有<span style=\"color: red;\">便衣警員混入示威者</span>，其聲稱要往警總上班，惟身上並<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有掛上委任證</span>，顯然違反此例。<br />\n於7月7日旺角清場行動中，大量警員身穿便服，頭戴警察頭盔，行動時沒有出示委任證，有市民懷疑其身份，並要求其出示委任證，警員答道「警員在執行職務時不需提供委任證」及「一組警員行動時只需一人出示委任證」等言辭，反映大量警員漠視守則，知法犯法。"},{"pid":"ff168011de5239e6b5fb65fd7a7bb963f5176984","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第26章第2(4)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFGWwi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFGWwi5.jpg&h=b1ca01ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《警察通例》規定，警方在接到市民投訴時，須清楚告知投訴人其投訴會記錄在案，並須通知投訴人警方所/將採取的行動，而且須向值日官報告。<br />\n於過去多次示威遊行中，多位市民曾向警員查詢如何投訴警察，惟警員只作簡單回應「監警會」及「投訴警察課」等。如此敷衍回應已經違反該條例，反映警方<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有對投訴作出妥善的回應及跟進</span>。"},{"pid":"7fad8bd3c99b67a0a4abc7135cf4ad12cb7f171e","tid":1303964,"uid":265703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"識都無用，d爛仔都唔會跟規矩做野!<br />\n而你又投訴無門<br />\n根本成個警察部門都都毫無紀律規則可言，可悲既係呢班爛仔係合法執法者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2816bab41156fe10a23cbc912e3c754cf5b1ba18","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"《警察通例》 第26章第2(7,8)條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJ6fMV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJ6fMV7.jpg&h=36db031f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVvwkf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVvwkf8.jpg&h=8e4e34f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於7月2日，監警會舉行記者會，表示會就近期事件展開調查。惟主席梁定邦表示若投訴人本身涉及違法行為，會將投訴人資料轉介至警方。此言論明顯違反《警察通例》，若投訴人就警方性質嚴重的不當行為進行投訴，案件檔案中<span style=\"color: red;\">無須記載與投訴人有關的資料</span>。監警會此等言論明顯引導或誘導警員在處理投訴時違反《警察通例》。"},{"pid":"fad102a758612992248f5fb25595cce1f93738d6","tid":1303964,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"要讓警隊(同背後的港共政權)失去合法性並非冇可能. <br />\n呢樣需要英國政府作為中英聯合聲明的監察方與簽約方做嘢.<br />\n所以點解強調N次要向英國申訴, 就係因為只有佢哋先有能力令呢個政權一夜之間變成&quot;非法組織&quot;.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3e51d93f106338b1bf3b74ef1126de816f7c3d","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fad8bd3c99b67a0a4abc7135cf4ad12cb7f171e","tid":1303964,"uid":265703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"識都無用，d爛仔都唔會跟規矩做野!<br />\n而你又投訴無門<br />\n根本成個警察部門都都毫無紀律規則可言，可悲既係呢班爛仔係合法執法者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"我認同作用不大，但同人拗都要拎出理據。文宣行動時可以作參考。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ba8d1e3753800cdb17303844b803f92830c14a","tid":1303964,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要嗰章<br />\nCh29 武力與槍械使用<br />\n係冇公開過!!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67c81b3e71265f7c340fd34b9fd979a3f0e1ca90","tid":1303964,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ba8d1e3753800cdb17303844b803f92830c14a","tid":1303964,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要嗰章<br />\nCh29 武力與槍械使用<br />\n係冇公開過!!!!</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:16:11.000Z","msg":"內部傳閱，真係搵唔到"},{"pid":"91d06d9f02ad4d49f3d7207a4a9360124169e245","tid":1303964,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"996be950d26a64ae0d1667a94c33ce14fc54f3e3","tid":1303964,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"點都投訴咗先，反正無成本"}]}